column16: Miguel Cabrera flies out to center fielder Mike Trout.

Rajai Davis walks.   Bryan Holaday to 3rd.    Andrew Romine to 2nd.
Andrew Romine walks.   Bryan Holaday to 2nd.
Bryan Holaday singles on a bunt ground ball to pitcher Josh Wall.
Nick Castellanos pops out to second baseman Howie Kendrick.
Nick Castellanos singles on a soft line drive to left fielder J.  B.   Shuck.   Rajai Davis scores.    Ian Kinsler to 3rd.    Nick Castellanos to 2nd on the throw.
Ian Kinsler singles on a line drive to right fielder Brennan Boesch.   Alex Avila scores.    Andrew Romine scores.    Rajai Davis to 3rd.
Rajai Davis singles on a line drive to left fielder J.  B.   Shuck.   Alex Avila to 3rd.    Andrew Romine to 2nd.
